    <item>
      <title>高盛提高薪酬成本，利润再次下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-05/goldman-bumps-up-pay-costs-as-profit-set-to-slump-again-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团首席财务官丹尼斯·科尔曼表示，尽管该行利润将再次下滑，但这家华尔街巨头的薪酬成本可能会以低至中个位数的百分比上涨。斯里达尔·纳塔拉詹 (Sridhar Natarajan) 接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-05/goldman-bumps-up-pay-costs-as-profit-set-to-slump-again-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 23:13:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国盈利状况恶化给了空头更多抛售理由</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/worsening-china-earnings-are-giving-bears-more-reasons-to-sell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国盈利疲软正在破灭股市反弹的希望，随着经济衰退似乎将持续下去，一些投资者准备迎接更多痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/worsening-china-earnings-are-giving-bears-more-reasons-to-sell</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾大中华ETF的破产显示金融脱钩的程度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/taiwan-s-big-china-etf-bust-shows-extent-of-financial-decoupling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着曾经全球最大的中国债券交易所交易基金市场几近崩溃，台湾与中国大陆的经济和金融脱钩进一步加深。]]></description>
