    <item>
      <title>美国银行莫伊尼汉：经济放缓，前景依然乐观（音频）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-05/bofa-s-moynihan-economy-slowing-outlook-still-positive-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官布赖恩·莫伊尼汉表示，他看到美国经济放缓的迹象，但该公司仍预计美国经济将软着陆，而不是陷入衰退。他在高盛美国金融服务会议上发表讲话。 （节选）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-05/bofa-s-moynihan-economy-slowing-outlook-still-positive-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:56:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市上涨，国债因美国就业机会上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/asia-stocks-to-gain-treasuries-rally-on-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场进一步放缓，加剧了人们对美联储明年将降息以防止经济衰退的猜测，从而刺激美国国债恢复涨势，亚洲股市将上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/asia-stocks-to-gain-treasuries-rally-on-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 22:47:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场押注欧洲央行将引领全球降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/markets-turbocharge-bets-that-ecb-will-lead-world-on-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该地区最鹰派的政策制定者之一将通胀放缓描述为“令人鼓舞”之后，投资者押注欧洲将引领全球最大的央行降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/markets-turbocharge-bets-that-ecb-will-lead-world-on-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场股票撤离中国的幅度为数十年来之最</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/emerging-market-stocks-leave-china-lagging-the-most-in-25-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，新兴市场股市下跌，其中中国公司领跌，这些公司的股价目前较发展中国家同行有四分之一个世纪以来的最大折价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/emerging-market-stocks-leave-china-lagging-the-most-in-25-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 12:46:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
