      <title>伦敦证券交易所三个月内第三次停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/london-stock-exchange-is-hit-by-third-outage-since-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦证券交易所集团 (London Stock Exchange Group Plc) 遭遇了几个月内的第三次停电，约 2,000 股较小型股票的交易被暂停，这加剧了该交易所运营商最近的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/london-stock-exchange-is-hit-by-third-outage-since-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 09:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
